@baseUrl = http://localhost:4000
@scenarioVersion = {{$timestamp}}

### Cadastro do usuario 1 (dono das transacoes) -> 201 sem corpo
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Maria da Silva",
  "email": "maria.transacoes.{{scenarioVersion}}@example.com",
  "password": "Strong@123"
}

### Login do usuario 1 -> 200 com token
# @name loginUser1
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "maria.transacoes.{{scenarioVersion}}@example.com",
  "password": "Strong@123"
}

### Cadastro do usuario 2 (usado para validar isolamento) -> 201 sem corpo
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Joao Pereira",
  "email": "joao.transacoes.{{scenarioVersion}}@example.com",
  "password": "Strong@123"
}

### Login do usuario 2 -> 200 com token
# @name loginUser2
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "joao.transacoes.{{scenarioVersion}}@example.com",
  "password": "Strong@123"
}

### Criacao de conta do usuario 1 -> 201
# @name createAccountUser1
POST {{baseUrl}}/accounts
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{loginUser1.response.body.token}}

{
  "name": "Carteira",
  "type": "wallet",
  "initialBalance": 0
}

### Criacao de conta do usuario 2 (para tentativa de invasao) -> 201
# @name createAccountUser2
POST {{baseUrl}}/accounts
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{loginUser2.response.body.token}}

{
  "name": "Carteira do Joao",
  "type": "wallet",
  "initialBalance": 0
}

### Criacao de categoria do usuario 1 -> 201
# @name createCategoryUser1
POST {{baseUrl}}/categories
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{loginUser1.response.body.token}}

{
  "name": "Mercado",
  "type": "expense",
  "color": "#059669"
}

### Criacao de categoria do usuario 2 (para tentativa de invasao) -> 201
# @name createCategoryUser2
POST {{baseUrl}}/categories
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{loginUser2.response.body.token}}

{
  "name": "Mercado do Joao",
  "type": "expense",
  "color": "#059669"
}

### Criacao de transacao valida (usuario 1) -> 201
# @name createTransaction
POST {{baseUrl}}/transactions
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{loginUser1.response.body.token}}

{
  "date": "2026-01-10T00:00:00.000Z",
  "description": "Compras do mes",
  "type": "expense",
  "amount": 350.75,
  "accountId": "{{createAccountUser1.response.body.id}}",
  "categoryId": "{{createCategoryUser1.response.body.id}}"
}

### Criacao de transacao de receita valida (usuario 1) -> 201
# @name createIncomeTransaction
POST {{baseUrl}}/transactions
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{loginUser1.response.body.token}}

{
  "date": "2026-02-05T00:00:00.000Z",
  "description": "Salario",
  "type": "income",
  "amount": 5000,
  "accountId": "{{createAccountUser1.response.body.id}}"
}

### Criacao de transacao com accountId de outro usuario -> 404 transaction.account.not.found
POST {{baseUrl}}/transactions
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{loginUser1.response.body.token}}

{
  "date": "2026-01-10T00:00:00.000Z",
  "description": "Tentativa de invasao",
  "type": "expense",
  "amount": 100,
  "accountId": "{{createAccountUser2.response.body.id}}"
}

### Criacao de transacao com categoryId de outro usuario -> 404 transaction.category.not.found
POST {{baseUrl}}/transactions
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{loginUser1.response.body.token}}

{
  "date": "2026-01-10T00:00:00.000Z",
  "description": "Tentativa de invasao",
  "type": "expense",
  "amount": 100,
  "accountId": "{{createAccountUser1.response.body.id}}",
  "categoryId": "{{createCategoryUser2.response.body.id}}"
}

### Criacao de transacao com amount negativo -> 422
POST {{baseUrl}}/transactions
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{loginUser1.response.body.token}}

{
  "date": "2026-01-10T00:00:00.000Z",
  "description": "Invalida",
  "type": "expense",
  "amount": -10,
  "accountId": "{{createAccountUser1.response.body.id}}"
}

### Criacao de transacao com type fora do enum -> 422
POST {{baseUrl}}/transactions
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{loginUser1.response.body.token}}

{
  "date": "2026-01-10T00:00:00.000Z",
  "description": "Invalida",
  "type": "outro",
  "amount": 100,
  "accountId": "{{createAccountUser1.response.body.id}}"
}

### Listagem de transacoes do usuario 1, sem filtros -> 200 com todas do usuario
GET {{baseUrl}}/transactions
Authorization: Bearer {{loginUser1.response.body.token}}

### Listagem de transacoes do usuario 2 -> 200 lista vazia (isolamento)
GET {{baseUrl}}/transactions
Authorization: Bearer {{loginUser2.response.body.token}}

### Listagem com filtro de periodo (retorna apenas a de janeiro) -> 200
GET {{baseUrl}}/transactions?from=2026-01-01&to=2026-01-31
Authorization: Bearer {{loginUser1.response.body.token}}

### Listagem com filtro de type=income -> 200 apenas a transacao de salario
GET {{baseUrl}}/transactions?type=income
Authorization: Bearer {{loginUser1.response.body.token}}

### Listagem com filtro de accountId -> 200
GET {{baseUrl}}/transactions?accountId={{createAccountUser1.response.body.id}}
Authorization: Bearer {{loginUser1.response.body.token}}

### Listagem com filtro de categoryId -> 200 apenas a transacao com categoria
GET {{baseUrl}}/transactions?categoryId={{createCategoryUser1.response.body.id}}
Authorization: Bearer {{loginUser1.response.body.token}}

### Listagem com paginacao (page=1, pageSize=1) -> 200 com 1 item e total >= 2
GET {{baseUrl}}/transactions?page=1&pageSize=1
Authorization: Bearer {{loginUser1.response.body.token}}

### Busca por id da transacao do usuario 1 -> 200
GET {{baseUrl}}/transactions/{{createTransaction.response.body.id}}
Authorization: Bearer {{loginUser1.response.body.token}}

### Busca por id inexistente -> 404 transaction.not.found
GET {{baseUrl}}/transactions/00000000-0000-4000-8000-000000000000
Authorization: Bearer {{loginUser1.response.body.token}}

### Busca da transacao do usuario 1 usando o token do usuario 2 -> 404 transaction.not.found (isolamento)
GET {{baseUrl}}/transactions/{{createTransaction.response.body.id}}
Authorization: Bearer {{loginUser2.response.body.token}}

### Atualizacao da transacao do usuario 1 -> 200
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/transactions/{{createTransaction.response.body.id}}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{loginUser1.response.body.token}}

{
  "description": "Compras do mes atualizado",
  "amount": 400
}

### Atualizacao com amount invalido -> 422
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/transactions/{{createTransaction.response.body.id}}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{loginUser1.response.body.token}}

{
  "amount": -5
}

### Atualizacao usando accountId de outro usuario -> 404 transaction.account.not.found
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/transactions/{{createTransaction.response.body.id}}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{loginUser1.response.body.token}}

{
  "accountId": "{{createAccountUser2.response.body.id}}"
}

### Atualizacao da transacao do usuario 1 usando o token do usuario 2 -> 404 transaction.not.found (isolamento)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/transactions/{{createTransaction.response.body.id}}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{loginUser2.response.body.token}}

{
  "description": "Tentativa de invasao"
}

### Exclusao de transacao inexistente -> 404 transaction.not.found
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/transactions/00000000-0000-4000-8000-000000000000
Authorization: Bearer {{loginUser1.response.body.token}}

### Exclusao da transacao do usuario 1 usando o token do usuario 2 -> 404 transaction.not.found (isolamento)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/transactions/{{createTransaction.response.body.id}}
Authorization: Bearer {{loginUser2.response.body.token}}

### Exclusao da transacao do usuario 1 -> 204 sem corpo
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/transactions/{{createTransaction.response.body.id}}
Authorization: Bearer {{loginUser1.response.body.token}}
